    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.46 / v0 + 0.64)) / ((v2 + 0.51 + v2 + 0.14) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.28)))
    tmp = (v1 * (tmp + 0.26))
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = wp.abs(0.91)
    v1 = wp.abs(0.70)
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.55) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.83)) - (0.37 / (v0 + 0.38 / v0 + 0.99)))
    data[tid] = v0
